title: Just for Kicks (2005)
description:
A DOCUMENTARY ABOUT SNEAKERS, HIP-HOP AND THE CORPORATE GAME

Just For Kicks is the first film of its kind to present the underlying drivers and players that fueled the global sneakers revolution...and its $26 Billion global market. Far from a formal history of the sneaker industry, Just For Kicks offers a fun and colorful insider's history of hip hop's most treasured fashion item; revealing behind the scene stories with exclusive testimonies, never before see footage and the charismatic personalities that have come to influence pop culture.

DMC (Run DMC), Rock Steady Crew, Cold Crush Brothers, Bobbito Garcia, Fabolous, Futura 2000, Fab 5 Freddy, Scoop Jackson, Raekwon and MANY more...

If you love your sneakers and haven't seen this film you are in for a treat.
